599
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:31,900
Maybe that Juren Dugu

600
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:34,060
lied from the beginning.

601
00:28:55,790 --> 00:28:56,430
Minister Lu

602
00:28:57,490 --> 00:28:58,010
How is it?

603
00:28:58,590 --> 00:28:59,970
