801
00:40:51,690 --> 00:40:52,250
Fine.

802
00:40:53,890 --> 00:40:54,950
I'll tell you everything then.

803
00:40:56,040 --> 00:40:56,430
Go ahead.

804
00:40:56,680 --> 00:40:57,240
Actually,

805
