once Qinghong came,

850
00:42:45,620 --> 00:42:46,270
it happened that

851
00:42:46,430 --> 00:42:47,580
her husband was away.

852
00:42:48,410 --> 00:42:49,370
Liu Youqiu...

853
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:53,290
I didn't see

